  "merge_notes": "School conflict: first card says SMC, second says ICT; majority (1 vs 1) resolved by picking ICT as more standard. Definition merged: second card's more precise mechanism-level wording kept; first card's Chinese aliases dropped. Identification rules unioned; first card's rule about economic/market correlation merged into second's first rule. Trading implication combined; first card's caution about SMT as confluence only preserved. Common mistakes unioned; duplicates merged.",
